  "remarks": "\nAli Akbar Salehi is an involved person within the meaning of the Iran (Sanctions) (Nuclear) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019. Ali Akbar Salehi is or has been responsible for, engaging in, providing support for, or promoting, or facilitating, the development of a nuclear weapon delivery system in, or for use in, Iran.\n",
